t_text:
Am sat here reflecting just how proud I am of my party.
Of its stance on Brexit before, during and after the referendum.
The @LibDems are, proudly and unapologetically, pro European. 
And, for all its imperfections, we are pro EU too. 
#Yes2EU #LibDems #DemandBetter

Parliament is sovereign.
If Parliament decides to stop #Brexit, it is entirely within its rights to do so.
I would, of course, welcome such a move.
#ExitFromBrexit #Yes2EU
